enter customer name: sravanthi
enter customer phone number: 9087654321
enter no of facewash:1
enter no of proteinx: 1
enter no of butter: 2
enter no of  shampoo: 1
enter no of vinegar: 0
bill: 1741
total bill amount:  2002.15
